Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:04.06,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一份蓝图，甚至一些备件\N{\fs13}A blueprint and even some spare parts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.13,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经为此准备好了\N{\fs13}for just such an adventure already existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.93,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}NASA 此前的伽利略任务，\N{\fs13}NASA's Galileo mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.27,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}向木星发射了一个轨道飞行器和一个探测器\N{\fs13}that sent an orbiter and a probe to Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.17,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欧洲和美国的支持者\N{\fs13}Advocates in Europe and the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.54,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}主张一个前往土星的类似任务，\N{\fs13}argued for a similar mission destined for Saturn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.68,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并使之成为一个国际合作项目\N{\fs13}one composed of an international consortium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.11,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有人知道\N{\fs13}How such a project with all its complexities
