Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.98,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与彗星会合小行星飞掠计划（CRAF），\N{\fs13}meant to rendezvous with a comet and an asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.65,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最终还是被取消了\N{\fs13}was unable to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.85,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}NASA 新规划的一部分\N{\fs13}This was part of a new NASA strategy to cut back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是缩减大型昂贵航天器的预算\N{\fs13}on large and expensive spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:19.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而卡西尼号的尺寸无法掩饰：\N{\fs13}*And there was no disguising Cassini's size.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.76,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至今为止，\N{\fs13}It remains, to this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.90,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它还是美国有史以来建造的最大的星际飞船\N{\fs13}the largest US interplanetary spacecraft ever built.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.14,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竖立时有三层楼高，\N{\fs13}Standing three stories tall, when fully loaded,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:31.34,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}满载时将重达1.25万磅（5.6 吨）\N{\fs13}it will weigh 12 and a half thousand pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.48,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第一次看没有被遮布掩盖的，\N{\fs13}- The first time I saw the spacecraft together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.48,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}组装完成的飞船时，\N{\fs13}when we stacked without the blankets,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:40.95,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我当时一定在游客走廊上站了有30分钟\N{\fs13}I must have stood in the visitor gallery for 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:45.09,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道怎么形容它\N{\fs13}And it's... I don't know how to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.15,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你知道，它不再属于你了\N{\fs13}It's not yours anymore, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:50.46,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}尽管我对每一个组件都很熟悉\N{\fs13}Even though I had been intimate with each piece
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.56,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一个接一个地\N{\fs13}and part of that spacecraft and put it together
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:55.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亲手把飞船组装起来，\N{\fs13}wire by wire and in part by part,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:59.40,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但看到它成为一个整体时还是感到不可思议\N{\fs13}to watch it come together as a whole entity was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.47,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们站在那，静默无言\N{\fs13}We were without words standing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.94,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们偶尔会在这里工作\N{\fs13}- Every now and then we'll be working in here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.48,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就会想，哇，这将飞往土星\N{\fs13}and you'll think, wow, this is going to Saturn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:11.95,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个探测器将降落在泰坦上\N{\fs13}and this probe is gonna land on Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.38,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是我们从未去过的地方\N{\fs13}And this is going somewhere where we've never
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.59,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想到这些，就会心潮澎湃\N{\fs13}seen things before and you get goosebumps from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.82,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宇宙飞船的设计\N{\fs13}- [Narrator] The spacecraft has been designed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.12,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}优先考虑了冗余\N{\fs13}with redundancy as a priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.59,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}每个关键系统都有一个相同的备份\N{\fs13}Each critical system has an identical backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:30.26,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其先进的软件将允许航天器\N{\fs13}And its advanced software will allow the spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.50,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在某些时候自主飞行，\N{\fs13}at times to fly on its own,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.77,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}甚至自我修复电脑故障\N{\fs13}and even self-repair computer glitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:44.38,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}卡西尼号内部有大约22000个线缆连接\N{\fs13}In Cassini's interior are some 22,000 wire connections
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.62,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有超过7英里的电缆\N{\fs13}and more than seven miles of cabling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.72,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}严格来说，我是一名工程助理，\N{\fs13}- I'm technically an engineering assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:55.22,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的工作是为宇宙飞船布线\N{\fs13}and what I do is cabling for the spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已经做了20年了\N{\fs13}and I've been doing it for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们机械团队的一个很大优点是\N{\fs13}One of the really positive points about our mechanical team
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:08.40,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是绝不放弃\N{\fs13}is that they never say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.37,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}团队似乎从不疲倦\N{\fs13}They never seem to tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.17,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总是很积极\N{\fs13}They're always up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:15.48,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们已经做到最好了\N{\fs13}(chuckles) I don't think we could ask for a better team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:23.48,new,,0,0,0,,*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.72,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最后一项装配任务包括\N{\fs13}- [Narrator] One of the last assembly tasks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:30.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用毯子盖住这个裸露的飞船\N{\fs13}is to cover this bare spacecraft with blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:36.33,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使用的机器常用于手工精细剪裁\N{\fs13}Using machines more often used for fine tailoring
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.30,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而非工业用途，\N{\fs13}than engineering,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.37,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用裁切过的反光材料在任务早期\N{\fs13}this reflective material is cut to protect the spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.34,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在飞向太阳时保护航天器\N{\fs13}early in the mission, when it flies toward the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.58,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种黑色织物的效果正好相反，\N{\fs13}This black fabric will do the opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.95,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在土星吸收和保持热量，\N{\fs13}absorbing and retaining heat out at Saturn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:57.58,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那里的阳光强度只有地球的1%\N{\fs13}where sunlight is only 1% the strength found at Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.82,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些保护层还将屏蔽那些\N{\fs13}The layers will also provide shielding
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.62,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}微小流星体\N{\fs13}from micro meteoroids,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.73,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及细小的灰尘颗粒\N{\fs13}tiny particles of dust that could damage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.83,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它们可能会损害宇宙飞船的电子设备\N{\fs13}the spacecraft's electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.17,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一项乏味的工作，\N{\fs13}This is tedious work,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.44,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}切割、缝合和装配\N{\fs13}cutting, stitching and fitting hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.97,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大量单独定制的工件\N{\fs13}of individually measured pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.74,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}考虑到这个“太空被子”非常精巧复杂，\N{\fs13}It is a job made even more challenging
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.11,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这项工作会更具挑战性\N{\fs13}knowing that this intricate space quilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.98,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像卡西尼号的所有主要部件一样，\N{\fs13}like all of Cassini's major components,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.98,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}必须拆卸才能运抵佛罗里达州，\N{\fs13}will have to be unmounted for shipping to Florida,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:34.15,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所有的东西都要在那里重新组装\N{\fs13}where everything will be reassembled again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.46,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们在卡西尼号上遇到的问题\N{\fs13}- We have had less problem with this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.63,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}比我记得的任何其他飞船上都要少\N{\fs13}than I can remember having on any other spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}难以置信\N{\fs13}*It's almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.03,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它真漂亮啊\N{\fs13}It's just beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.30,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有碰上大麻烦\N{\fs13}No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:47.10,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最多只是些小问题\N{\fs13}No major problems anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.61,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}依据卡西尼号的蓝图\N{\fs13}- [Narrator] While transforming Cassini from a blueprint
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:57.98,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}建造出一艘真正的宇宙飞船的过程非常顺利，\N{\fs13}into a real spacecraft had gone exceptionally well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:01.58,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但敲定最终设计的过程却备受折磨\N{\fs13}getting to the final design had been torturous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.72,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遭遇预算削减，该项目被迫\N{\fs13}Facing budget cuts, the project was forced
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:11.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做出另一个无奈之举\N{\fs13}to make another least unacceptable decision*.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.96,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了不减少科学仪器，\N{\fs13}Instead of dropping science instruments,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.53,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}飞船的尺寸被缩小，\N{\fs13}the spacecraft itself was scaled back by eliminating
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.17,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}取消了扫描平台，\N{\fs13}the scan platform,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.47,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个平台是一种转盘\N{\fs13}a kind of turntable required by some instruments
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.07,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搭载某些需要移动的仪器\N{\fs13}needing motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.61,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有了平台，\N{\fs13}Without the platform, the entire spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.24,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}探测器需要通过整体旋转来瞄准目标，\N{\fs13}will have to rotate to aim at targets,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.85,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这减少了观测时间\N{\fs13}resulting also in less observation time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.55,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但所有的科学仪器都保留了下来\N{\fs13}But all of the science instruments have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.03,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}卡西尼-惠更斯号\N{\fs13}Operations are now almost complete
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.63,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即将发射\N{\fs13}for the launch of Cassini Huygens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.00,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发射台上是空军的\N{\fs13}Already on the launch pad is the Air Force's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:59.81,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大力神4号B型运载火箭\N{\fs13}heavy lifting Titan 4B
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.61,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}卡西尼号和探测器已经重新组装\N{\fs13}Cassini and the probe have been reassembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.02,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最后一道程序包括\N{\fs13}One of the last procedures involves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.32,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}将其电源加装到航天器上，\N{\fs13}loading onto the spacecraft its power supply,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:17.16,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}72磅钚被封装在\N{\fs13}72 pounds of plutonium encased in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:21.49,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放射性同位素热电发电机中，\N{\fs13}what are called radio isotope thermoelectric generators,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:25.47,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者缩写为 RTG\N{\fs13}or mercifully called for short RTGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:33.11,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}RTG 在以前的任务中使用过，\N{\fs13}RTGs have been used on previous missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:37.48,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是最近的核电站事故\N{\fs13}but recent nuclear power plant accidents
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.35,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有挑战者号航天飞机的失利\N{\fs13}and the loss of the Space Shuttle Challenger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.95,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}加剧了公众对发射事故\N{\fs13}have heightened public fears of a launch accident
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.89,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}会扩散核物质碎片的恐惧\N{\fs13}spreading nuclear debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.56,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了终止发射，\N{\fs13}Hoping to stop the launch,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:55.26,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反核组织提起诉讼，向白宫请愿，\N{\fs13}anti-nuclear groups file lawsuits, petition the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.93,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并在肯尼迪航天中心举行示威\N{\fs13}and hold demonstrations at the Kennedy Space Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.44,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是最后的机会在公开对话中向大家保证\N{\fs13}- Since this is the last  to ensure the public
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.47,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这次不会发生事故\N{\fs13}that everything is going to be all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.97,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你能最后一次\N{\fs13}could you do that one last time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.14,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用最好的论据去说服，\N{\fs13}and use your best argument to persuade,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:11.08,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的反对者们吗\N{\fs13}perhaps, some of your opponents?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.45,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}RTG的设计考虑到了发生事故的情况\N{\fs13}- RTGs were designed for accident conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.78,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们设计并测试，\N{\fs13}We've designed them, we've tested them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:16.68,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经进行分析，而且经历过了\N{\fs13}we've analyzed for it, we've gone through
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.55,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一个非常漫长的审查过程\N{\fs13}a very lengthy review process.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:21.52,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}事实上，这些都是非常安全的\N{\fs13}And in fact, these are very safe to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.89,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对公众没有风险，\N{\fs13}There's not a risk to the public,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.66,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即使发生事故也是如此\N{\fs13}even if there is an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.46,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们能确认你们对这次任务的信心吗\N{\fs13}- Would you all confirm your faith in this mission
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:32.00,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}告诉我们有多少你的家庭成员，孩子，\N{\fs13}by telling us how many family members, kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:36.64,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有孙子孙女一起看这次发布会？\N{\fs13}and grandkids you have here watching this launch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.81,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我在这里有30个家庭成员，\N{\fs13}- Well, I have 30 members of my family here right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.04,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}包括我的两个孙女\N{\fs13}including my two granddaughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.54,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能还将有更多孩子即将出世\N{\fs13}There's more on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.65,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道我是否会有更多的孙子孙女，\N{\fs13}I don't know if I have more grandchildren on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:51.85,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但确实会有更多的家庭成员\N{\fs13}but I have more family on the way*.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:56.19,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现实是，当下\N{\fs13}The reality is there's no technology on the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:59.53,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及在可预见的将来\N{\fs13}that has the promise to be available
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:02.13,new,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有任何其他技术可以确保\N{\fs13}in the foreseeable future at all
